{"id": "Qme1eCWgF7pwyyXRr8AL7JtwWHLX249cj9Fkfzupwdzqvy", "title": "Upgrade the ADX Loyalty pool price ladder", "body": "## Retrospective\nThe ADX-LOYALTY pool price ladder is a mechanism that adjusts the APY according to the ADX price. \n\nThe underlying concept is:\n* Create a positive feedback loop that rewards holders when the price is high and incentivizes them to keep holding\n* In a bull market where ADX is uptrending, issuance is justified, as it helps our marketing, keeps our APYs competitive, and does not damage confidence\n* In a bear market, tokens with low or negative issuance are appreciated more\n\nSee this article on how it works: https://help.adex.network/hc/en-us/articles/360017158819-Understanding-The-ADX-Loyalty-Pool-and-Elastic-Issuance\n\n## Proposal\n\nCurrently, ADX is not perceived to be in an uptrend, but according to the old price ladder, the current price is still on one of the highest steps at 35% APY.\n\nWe're proposing that this new price ladder becomes active on the 27th of July:\n* Up to $0.05: 5% APY\n* Up to $0.10: 10% APY\n* Up to $0.20: 20% APY\n* Up to $0.35: 25% APY\n* Up to $0.50: 30% APY\n* Up to $1.00: 35% APY\n* Up to $2.00: 38% APY\n* Up to $2.50: 40% APY\n* More: 40% APY\n\nThis also ensures that the loyalty pool does not compete with the Tom pool\n\n## Voting\n\nTom pool holders can now also vote on this proposal. \n\nThe voting power depends on the amount of staking tokens that you have (ADX-LOYALTY and ADX-STAKING), which favors early stakers over later stakers, since those are share tokens.\n\nFor example, if you staked early, going in with 10 ADX issues you 10 ADX-STAKING. But after the pool has already incurred 20% rewards, 10 ADX issues you 10/1.2 ADX-STAKING.\n\n## Timeline\n\n* Voting: 20.07.2021 - 27.07.2021\n* Implementation and deploying: 27.07.2021", "choices": ["Yes", "No"], "start": 1626764400, "end": 1627392600, "snapshot": "12909000", "state": "closed", "author": "0xd6e371526cdaeE04cd8AF225D42e37Bc14688D9E", "space": {"id": "adex.eth", "name": "AdEx Network"}, "votes": 32, "votes_data": [{"id": "QmNkXxidt8Dy8cGtZ6iY6kZvzYnHouG4hcpZsVpAiB9pmm", "voter": "0xFa569479F8B4ef6F170E86C1FACEf085b9C118E4", "created": 1627392486, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "adex.eth"}}, {"id": "QmXmYgsKHdyFEurmJ7giU34tNohzAUngozNjbR5y819vNz", "voter": "0x0CF852CBE2a3eEe0aa76E92DA734c2c0752a7e54", "created": 1627377008, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "adex.eth"}}, {"id": "QmYYYeejxnhTWPi7WA4G3cPZKBfBVADV2ndc23Xb6QaWzZ", "voter": "0x0A8fe6e91eaAb3758dF18f546f7364343667E957", "created": 1627376156, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "adex.eth"}}, {"id": "QmWh9erXZR22xGvzi9eoneUmh9Ld4MLxk26PsmMbZgvf7T", "voter": "0x2aecF52ABe359820c48986046959B4136AfDfbe2", "created": 1627376124, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "adex.eth"}}, {"id": "QmfJAZg8nxbQ5CwAY77MGcctLFg5zaVNNa9gSiEeGGuaBv", "voter": "0x62e98142CA4f5bf2528F529EA11C71943872381F", "created": 1627375807, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "adex.eth"}}, {"id": "QmQSiETb48Bjru7SAgEvDzZD5HyvB1bRnopdxbiGEu1hGx", "voter": "0x2d2b4013536d801843653B8cD9aC4eD2D7042950", "created": 1627232738, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "adex.eth"}}, {"id": "QmZEPcFuybTupQovycRJByn5JGWeVpoCUWz4CUzy9R8PnH", "voter": "0x9e97E2A580E4B8166035eb2c103f296e311E87DB", "created": 1627058808, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "adex.eth"}}, {"id": "QmYEg2K4G75CFyVEbAnGb2x5MwjwmJTt6mu1iMNhW3z5YY", "voter": "0xb8967e3880135c2CA8E80f9edcCBb906e05B43fb", "created": 1626985926, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "adex.eth"}}, {"id": "QmYhWRjVw7GU6s8CmVXJtEKcL4uHXSF8Y5D5g33tLfZEeF", "voter": "0x3C3Ee0820eEa3abbaDDd2c01253f4E3A6Da37259", "created": 1626951913, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "adex.eth"}}, {"id": "QmdWga9VZUB2XM3Vj5R3Smg8kgpSNe6FBByExAAutk4gRr", "voter": "0x137F41ca27F570D4c50E56D5c20AE2807225F09C", "created": 1626916532, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "adex.eth"}}, {"id": "QmWi7ydu5qUiBhzmKhe8gZiy6PXEi8rVHDHx64S4u37gNx", "voter": "0xEca5aA947466E4E31e9b8087Ac811578064eC430", "created": 1626908856, "